title: Siva

creator: Siva Service Network Ltd
descriptionHtml:
Siva is the first social network that makes it easy for creators to share, earn money and monetize content.

We believe anyone with a skill who is willing to work should be able to make a decent living regardless of who they are or what they do. We hope to achieve that with Siva.

Creators are frustrated with traditional social networks. They don’t support creators. They don’t share their ad revenue. They don't let you reach most of your followers. To make it worse, they change their algorithm without caring about how this changes affect people's lives and businesses in the process.

Creators are building communities in other places. But these platforms don’t have enough users, or don't have enough advertising money to get creators paid. Creators need a leading social network that puts them first. A place where creators earn real money from ads & other monetization tools. That's why we are building Siva.
descriptionShort: Siva is a social app designed to help creators become financially independent.

title: Siva - Power to the Person

creator: Siva App
descriptionHtml:
Siva is a new kind of social network where every user gets their own coin and earn money from other people's success.

We make it easy to support creators when they are starting out and earn money from their rise.

Your profile will automatically generate a unique coin that can be bought and sold by the community. When people buy your coin, the price goes up. It's like having your own Bitcoin that anyone can purchase.

With your coin, you'll be able to incentivize anyone to help you achieve your goals. By having a share of your success, your community is motivated to help you grow and promote your work.
descriptionShort: We make it easy to support people early and earn money from their rise.
